        <p>
			Four years ago, Sanjivani Hospital &amp; Medical Research Institute opened its doors with the objective to strengthen medical care in the communities we serve, and empower patients&mdash;and their families&mdash;to make informed choices. 
			Looking back, it is indeed heartening to see that we have managed to live up to the very high ethical and professional standards we set ourselves upon inception, and meet the stringent benchmarks that characterise the finest medical institutions across the world. Further, we have succeeded in blazing a very individual trail by pursuing a full-time specialist system, and achieved a convergence of global best practices adapted to Indian needs with a family of healthcare professionals that combines talent, technical expertise and commitment across disciplines.<br /><br/>
			
			Our 11 &lsquo;centres of excellence&rsquo; have raised the bar in terms of diagnostics and treatment, and become destinations of choice for healthcare seekers in the know. Each complicated procedure undertaken, each successful outcome, only spurs the team on to greater heights, further innovation, the pursuit of excellence.<br />
			<br /><br/><br/>
			Our journey continues in a bid to reach more people, to touch&mdash;and save&mdash;more lives. And in this journey, the intangible rewards are often the greatest: the joy in the eyes of the parents whose newborn has successfully undergone congenital heart surgery; the easy gait of the silver man whose Parkinson&rsquo;s disease has responded to deep brain stimulation.<br />
			<br />
			These are just some of the successes that drive our committed, passionate team and make us strive harder to be the best we can be&mdash;and give Indians the best medical care they deserve.<br />
			This website is a key enabler in this journey, helping us to connect to the communities that nourish us. Aimed to reflect the cutting-edge technologies and international standards that distinguish Sanjivani Hospital &amp; Medical Research Institute, the site offers an interactive experience that will help you know and understand us better.<br />
			<br />
			Welcome to the future of healthcare!</p>
